comments.body:
Patch looks mostly good to me. Minor nits -

1)
{code}
      if (LOG.isInfoEnabled()) {
        LOG.info("no resource restrictions specified. not using docker's "
            + "cgroup options");
      }
    } else {
      if (LOG.isInfoEnabled()) {
        LOG.info("using docker's cgroups options");
      }
{code}
and 
{code}
      if (LOG.isInfoEnabled()) {
        LOG.info("using cgroup parent: " + cGroupPath);
      }
{code}

Maybe these should be log level debug? Seems like a lot of logging for info level.

2)
{code}
    String resourceOptionsCpu = "/sys/fs/cgroup/" + hierarchy + "/cpu/" +
        containerIdStr;
{code}
It shouldn't affect the test but shoudn't it be "/sys/fs/cgroup/cpu/" + hierarchy + "/" + containerIdStr ?

